There was jubilation on Tuesday when ace comic act John Okafor aka Mr Ibu was discharged from the hospital. Mr Ibu was hospitalised over suspected poisoning with the actor raising the alarm that some unscrupulous elements were using his illness to scam Nigerians.   Comedian MC Morris yanks off Portable from show     Sacked promoter cuts ties with Portable     Girl who touched singer Ruger inappropriately speaks out   In a new video on Tuesday, Mr Ibu said he was getting ready for discharge after treatment. He wrote: “Set to be discharged from the hospital, getting my hair cut. Praise God!”